{
  "page": "Sigorn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Thenn\" title=\"House Thenn\"><img alt=\"House Thenn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Thenn.svg/50px-House_Thenn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Thenn.svg/75px-House_Thenn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/House_Thenn.svg/100px-House_Thenn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Magnar</span><br />Sigorn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Thenn\" title=\"House Thenn\"><img alt=\"House Thenn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Thenn.svg/50px-House_Thenn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Thenn.svg/75px-House_Thenn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/House_Thenn.svg/100px-House_Thenn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sigorn by Denis Maznev.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg/350px-Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg/525px-Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg/700px-Sigorn_by_Denis_Maznev.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Sigorn, by Denis Maznev ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Magnar_of_Thenn\" title=\"Magnar of Thenn\">Magnar of Thenn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Thenns\" title=\"Thenns\">Thenns</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Thenn\" title=\"House Thenn\">House Thenn</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">Free folk</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Thenn_(valley)\" title=\"Thenn (valley)\">Thenn</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsigorn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsigorn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sigorn</b> is the son of <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Magnar_of_Thenn\" title=\"Magnar of Thenn\">Magnar of Thenn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Sigorn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Sigorn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Sigorn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Sigorn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Sigorn\" title=\"Category:Images of Sigorn\">Images of Sigorn</a></div>\n<p>Sigorn is said to look like his father <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a>, albeit younger and shorter. He is lean, with grey eyes, and has a receding hairline that makes him look older than his years. He wears <a href=\"/index.php/Bronze\" title=\"Bronze\">bronze</a> greaves and a leather shirt sewn with bronze scales.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Sigorn wields a bronze <a href=\"/index.php/Sword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sword\">sword</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Sigorn and his people take pride in the fact that they are <a href=\"/index.php/Thenns\" title=\"Thenns\">Thenns</a>, who have <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Laws\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Laws\">laws</a>, unlike the other <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Sigorn haltingly speaks the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a> with a thick accent.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After the death of his father, <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a>, during the <a href=\"/index.php/Attack_on_Castle_Black\" title=\"Attack on Castle Black\">attack on Castle Black</a>, Sigorn inherits the title <a href=\"/index.php/Magnar_of_Thenn\" title=\"Magnar of Thenn\">Magnar of Thenn</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and is taken captive by <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos76.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos76.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/34/Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg/350px-Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/34/Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg/525px-Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/34/Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg/700px-Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alys_x_sigorn_by_chillyravenart.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a> and Sigorn, by Chillyravenart ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Sigorn kneels before Stannis after passing through the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> It is rumored at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a> that Stannis intends to give lands and castles to Sigorn and <a href=\"/index.php/Rattleshirt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rattleshirt\">Rattleshirt</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Sigorn is reluctant to join the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> after the death of his father.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Emmett\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Iron Emmett\">Iron Emmett</a> advises <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a>, to grant a castle to the new Magnar of Thenn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Jon eventually devises a plan to wed Sigorn to <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a>, the current heir of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrion_Karstark\" title=\"Harrion Karstark\">Harrion Karstark</a>, the rightful <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Karhold\" title=\"Lord of Karhold\">Lord of Karhold</a>, which creates the new <a href=\"/index.php/House_Thenn\" title=\"House Thenn\">House Thenn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Alys has fled before a forced marriage arranged by her great-uncle, <a href=\"/index.php/Arnolf_Karstark\" title=\"Arnolf Karstark\">Arnolf Karstark</a>, to his son, <a href=\"/index.php/Cregan_Karstark\" title=\"Cregan Karstark\">Cregan</a>, in order to claim <a href=\"/index.php/Karhold\" title=\"Karhold\">Karhold</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Alys believes that Karhold will yield to her and Sigorn's two hundred <a href=\"/index.php/Thenns\" title=\"Thenns\">Thenns</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Sigorn_and_Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Wedding of Sigorn and Alys Karstark\">the wedding</a>, which is performed at Castle Black by <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a>, Sigorn leaps across a flaming ditch with his new bride.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Sigorn is initially reluctant to dance during the wedding feast, but he joins Alys after becoming inebriated from mulled <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Jon notes that despite his fierceness, Sigorn is surprisingly tender with his new wife.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Sigorn\">Quotes by Sigorn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Sigorn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Fight for you? Not fight for you. Kill you better. Kill all you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Sigorn, to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Melisandre</b>: Sigorn, will you share your fire with <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys</a>, and warm her when the night is dark and full of terrors?<br />\n</p><p><b>Sigorn</b>: I swear me. By the <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">red god's</a> flames, I warm her all her days.<br />\n<b>Melisandre</b>: Alys, do you swear to share your fire with Sigorn, and warm him when the night is dark and full of terrors?<br />\n<b>Alys</b>: Till his blood is boiling.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Melisandre</b>: Then come to me and be as one.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a>, Sigorn, and <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Sigorn\">Quotes about Sigorn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Sigorn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jon</b>: You're not scared?<br />\n</p><p><b>Alys</b>: Let him be scared of me.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Jon</b>: Winter's lady.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jon</b>: If <a href=\"/index.php/Harrion_Karstark\" title=\"Harrion Karstark\">her brother</a> is dead, <a href=\"/index.php/Karhold\" title=\"Karhold\">Karhold</a> belongs to Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys</a>. And she has given her hand in <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriage</a> to Sigorn, <a href=\"/index.php/Magnar_of_Thenn\" title=\"Magnar of Thenn\">Magnar of Thenn</a>.<br />\n<b>Cregan</b>: A <a href=\"/index.php/Wildling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildling\">wildling</a>. A filthy, murdering wilding. I see what you are, Snow. Half a <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">wolf</a> and half a wildling, <a href=\"/index.php/Baseborn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Baseborn\">baseborn</a> get of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">a traitor</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Whore\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whore\">whore</a>. You would deliver a <a href=\"/index.php/Highborn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Highborn\">highborn</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Maid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maid\">maid</a> to the bed of some stinking savage.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Cregan_Karstark\" title=\"Cregan Karstark\">Cregan Karstark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>A <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">northern maid</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Wildling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildling\">wildling</a> warrior, bound together by the <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">Lord of Light</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Axell_Florent\" title=\"Axell Florent\">Axell Florent</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafsigorn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafsigorn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Sigorn.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_10\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 10\">Chapter 10</a>, Jon III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">4.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\">4.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\">4.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\">4.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\">4.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\">4.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-8\">4.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-9\">4.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-10\">4.10</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_49\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 49\">Chapter 49</a>, Jon X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\">5.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Jon IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos76.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos76.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_76\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 76\">Chapter 76</a>, Jon XI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 35\">Chapter 35</a>, Jon VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Jon IX.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:cente